1
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,400
And the reason they could blackmail you

2
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:14,000
is because

3
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,039
they knew about your unbearable past,

4
00:01:16,039 --> 00:01:17,720
knew you killed Guan Jing,

5
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:18,280
and knew

6
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,240
you wouldn't miss such a good

7
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:22,100
opportunity to change your life.

8
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:23,600
Right?

9
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:25,880
Oh!

10
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:27,480
This ring is pretty.

11
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:27,960
No way.

12
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,039
This is my engagement ring.

13
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:30,400
Engagement ring?

14
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,000
Let go.

15
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:31,730
Give it to me.

16
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:32,930
Give it to me.

17
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:36,479
Li Ting,

18
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:39,720
you'd better think about what you did in the past.

19
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,840
What's dirty is dirty.

20
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,840
It can never be washed clean.

21
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:50,240
Their increasingly insatiable appetites,

22
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,600
to you, who already have one foot

23
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:53,479
in the upper circle,

24
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,960
are nothing short of a ticking time bomb.

25
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,160
As your wedding approaches,

26
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,080
their threat to you

27
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:06,200
makes you feel increasingly suffocated and broken.

28
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,260
Getting rid of them

29
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,720
is imminent.

30
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,720
But happiness is right in front of you.

31
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,760
Of course you wouldn't dirty your own hands.

32
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:15,120
You hated Zhou Guannan for abandoning you.

33
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,840
And for him,

34
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,720
you no longer had any feelings.

35
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,800
So you used his guilt towards you

36
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,140
to manipulate him,

37
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:24,079
and made up a whole new story about Guan Jing's death

38
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,040
to provoke him.

39
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,460
Actually, the day we met in the flower field,

40
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,260
I didn't tell you everything.

41
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,280
I said I wanted to die

42
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,120
because of the humiliation.

43
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:37,079
But it was also because of Guan Jing.

44
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,480
They pressed my head against the coffee table

45
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,720
and forced me to watch

46
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,800
Guan Jing being tortured to death.

47
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,220
Her eyes were wide open at the end,

48
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,880
terrifyingly hollow.

49
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,530
For all these years,

50
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,200
those eyes

51
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,400
have been pinned in my mind.

52
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,420
She kept looking at me.

53
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,600
They don't deserve to be human,

54
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:04,420
nor do they deserve to live in this world.

55
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,360
Just to cover up your past,

56
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:07,920
you

57
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,580
tricked Zhou Guannan into killing them.

58
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,640
I've suffered enough.

59
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,960
But before I go see her,

60
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,600
I must do something for her.

61
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,480
I should get back

62
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,500
a blood debt for Guan Jing.

63
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,200
For her,

64
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,560
and for ourselves.

65
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,360
Right?

66
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:31,480
Right.

67
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,360
Then do you dare?

68
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,000
Of course I do.

69
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:45,079
I didn't.

70
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,400
I really didn't kill anyone.

71
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,600
Zhou Guannan covered up your crimes

72
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,329
and committed suicide for you.

73
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,500
Don't you feel any guilt towards him?

74
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,440
Do you know what Li Ting said?

75
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:00,280
Zhou Guannan killed someone.

76
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,760
He committed suicide to escape punishment.

77
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,400
Isn't that a good thing?

78
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,520
What does this have to do with me?

79
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,440
Why did you bring me here?

80
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,400
Mr. Yan once told us both,

81
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,880
he said if you can't outsmart someone,

82
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,660
then use emotions.

83
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,720
Zhou Guannan, you are so smart,

84
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:26,460
but she played you for a fool with your feelings.

85
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,120
What you thought was revenge

86
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,520
and carrying out justice

87
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,920
was just a lie she told to coax you

88
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,080
into killing for her

89
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:36,080
and clearing the obstacles on her way to becoming a rich wife.

90
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,200
You are ridiculously wrong.

91
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,520
You were making meaningless sacrifices

92
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,720
for an illusion.

93
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,640
You wanted to live a good life,

94
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,300
but you killed so many people.

95
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,920
How can you still smile?

96
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,080
People always want to move up

97
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,720
and look up.

98
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,720
Anyway, I didn't break the law.

99
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,480
Go investigate.

100
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,280
I believe the law

101
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,410
will definitely clear my name, right?

102
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,200
There's one more person.

103
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,840
Like your father,

104
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,060
he is a police officer.

105
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,530
His name is Jia Peng.

106
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,570
Twenty-five years old.

107
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:18,080
He wasn't much younger than you.

108
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:23,120
But because of your boring game,

109
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,280
he closed his eyes forever.

110
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,760
Zhou Guannan, how many more lives will you destroy?

111
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,440
Tell me.

112
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:37,290
Are you going to keep making mistakes?

113
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,500
Now take another look at this person.

114
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:47,140
Think about what she really brought you.

115
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,460
Was it a few lies about shared suffering,

116
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,720
a few tears of shared hatred,

117
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,360
or an elaborate scheme,

118
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,540
deceiving you from start to finish to do her dirty work?

119
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,560
Zhou Guannan.

120
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,520
The word 'sacrifice',

121
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,120
do you really understand it?

122
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,080
Sacrifice is what your parents did,

123
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,800
suffering and working hard for you.

124
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,880
Sacrifice is what Jia Peng did,

125
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,680
risking his life to catch the real culprit.

126
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,440
But you,

127
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,920
were just bewitched by a woman,

128
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,520
and foolishly gave up your life

129
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,200
and soul,

130
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,920
along with the last bit of decency

131
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,480
your parents earned for you,

132
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:24,010
all to become someone else's stepping stone.

133
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,520
Why did she lie to me?

134
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,800
How could she lie to me?

135
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,140
You think with Zhou Guannan dead,

136
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,880
there's no evidence

137
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,520
pointing to you,

138
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,520
right?

139
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,080
But what if Zhou Guannan

140
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,920
isn't dead?

141
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,130
What do you mean?

142
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,130
Brother Yan,

143
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,130
Zhou Guannan's statement.

144
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,280
What do you mean?

145
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,040
Zhou Guannan has confessed.

146
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,840
Everything started at the flower shop.

147
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:46,640
On the day Qiao Sisi and Kong Jiao threatened you,

148
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,159
you decided to kill them.

149
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:48,920
I didn't.

150
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,840
You made yourself out to be Guan Jing's best friend,

151
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,080
instead of the one who persecuted her.

152
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:52,640
I didn't.

153
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,280
Under the false pretense of justice,

154
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:56,080
you tricked Zhou Guannan into killing for you.

155
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:56,760
I didn't.

156
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,680
I never wanted to kill anyone.

157
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,400
They forced me to do it.

158
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,720
I was about to have money.

159
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,440
I was about to enter high society

160
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,080
and start enjoying my life.

161
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,520
It was them.

162
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,880
They blackmailed me.

163
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,440
They threatened me,

164
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,640
demanded money,

165
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,240
and kept asking for more endlessly.

166
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,600
If they didn't die, my life would be a living hell.

167
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,200
What about Zhang Biao

168
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,080
and Wang Hongjia?

169
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,040
Did they blackmail you?

170
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,600
Not right now,

171
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,680
but they would have later.

172
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:31,120
The only ones who can keep a secret are the dead.

173
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,500
Same for Zhou Guannan,

174
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,600
right?

175
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,580
You tricked him into killing himself

176
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,240
just so he would

177
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,760
keep your secret.

178
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,080
Every man for himself.

179
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,920
You'd do the same if you were me.

180
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,020
No, I wouldn't.

181
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,440
You're not me.

182
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,200
You haven't been through it,

183
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,600
so you don't understand.

184
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,400
Do you really

185
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,240
understand it yourself?

186
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,040
Xun,

187
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,440
I disappointed you and Mi.

188
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,600
Next time you visit my parents,

189
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:46,040
don't tell them.

190
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,200
Now I announce

191
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,130
that the 5.17 major serial murder case

192
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,800
has been

193
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,780
successfully solved.

194
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,850
Don't celebrate too early.

195
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,290
This is the final stage.

196
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,640
Don't make any mistakes.

197
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:28,810
Especially you.

198
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,080
I will.

199
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:31,290
Alright.

200
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,200
Take it.

201
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,720
What is it?

202
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,600
A bonus.

203
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,560
There's a bonus?

204
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,440
Thank you, Chief.

205
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:04,610
You are truly a good apprentice trained by Zhou Gang.

206
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,040
This case.

207
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,640
We solved this together.

208
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,290
We put the chain of evidence together.

209
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:27,560
Rest assured.

210
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,560
There won't be any mistakes.

211
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,200
Exactly.

212
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:32,100
Since Brother Yan said so.

213
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:32,680
Captain,

214
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,560
just put your

215
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,520
mind at ease.

216
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,760
Everyone has

217
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,090
worked hard lately.

218
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,360
It's my treat tonight

219
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,660
at Yinhai Restaurant.

220
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:41,880
Brother Yan.

221
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:44,360
You are sounding more and more like Captain Sun.

222
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:44,800
Ah,

223
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,440
is that so?

224
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,720
You two are

225
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,960
exactly the same.

226
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,840
Let's go now.

227
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,720
Thanks, Yan.

228
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,360
Let's go.

229
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,400
Time to eat.

230
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:01,520
Zhou Guannan.

231
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:11,040
Here.

232
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:31,200
Time

233
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,460
always moves forward.

234
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,960
We can't always be stuck in the past.

235
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,960
We have to move on.

236
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:37,080
But some time

237
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,920
just doesn't move on.

238
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,320
Your time

239
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,800
can move forward now.

240
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:58,880
Sun.

241
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,200
Thank you.
